            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>小鵬汽車香港盛大活動全新 X9 亮相    CEO 何小鵬現身發佈會，展示全系列電動車</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/16/xpeng-global-brand-night/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=xpeng-global-brand-night</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/16/xpeng-global-brand-night/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 16 Apr 2025 04:00:24 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[X9]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[XPENG]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小鵬]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小鵬匯天]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[自動泊車]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遙控泊車]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[飛天車]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1303455</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div dir="auto">XPENG 小鵬汽車在香港首次舉利「小鵬全球熱愛之夜」品牌活動，廠方邀請了全球超過 500 位記者及本地的 VIP 車主到場參與，會上除展出小鵬全線電動車系及最新技術外，更發表全新 2025 款小鵬 X9 旗艦七座 MPV 新車，小鵬汽車創辦人何小鵬更親自到場發表演説，分享公司旗下的電動車、飛天車、機械人及 AI 汽車的發展趨勢。</div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303489" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_184106-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_184106-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_184106-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto">XPENG 於展德郵輪碼頭展出了品牌旗下全系列逾 20 款最新電動車，當中包括最新推出的 2025 款 X9、P7+、G6、G9 及 M03 等。此外，同場亦展出了小鵬匯天「陸地航母」飛天車、讓用戶可以率先體驗全自動泊車及手機遙控泊車等嶄新功能。同場亦劃分了多個不同展區，讓在場人士體驗 X9 在不同主題下寬敞車箱空間在精心佈置下的可朔性、及 X9 中排零重力座椅的體驗區。會上廠方人員透露 X9 已通過運輸署檢驗遙控泊車功能，相信很快可以透過 OTA 更新為車身龐大的 X9 車主提供這個方便實用的功能。</div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303491" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_190523-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_190523-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_190523-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div dir="auto" style="text-align: center;">小鵬汽車創辦人何小鵬親自到場發表長達演説</div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303494" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_171216-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_171216-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_171216-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303488" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_185004-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_185004-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_185004-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303485" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_185744-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_185744-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_185744-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303498" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_172836-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_172836-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_172836-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto">2025 最新版本的 X9 七座電動 MPV 外型上沒有太大變動，主要針對車箱空間及舒適性進行升級，當中包括新設計的兩張中排座椅加入一鍵零重力模式、同時備有手機無線功能、及座位上金屬質感的功能面板等等。新版 X9 「一換一」車價分別為標準版 HK$599,900(84.5kWh 標準版) 及長續航版 HK$639,900(101.5kWh 長續航版) 起，分別可以提供 500km 及 590km 續航力（WLTP 標準）。此外，廠方亦提供包括豪華內裝套裝的限量 Phantom Edition 版本，售價為 HK$679,900 起。</div><div dir="auto"></div><div dir="auto"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303496" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_171010-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_171010-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_20250415_171010-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div dir="auto" style="text-align: center;">雖然未有提供試飛，不過小鵬匯天「陸地航母」飛天車亦是場中另一焦點</div><div dir="auto"></div><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
